e is another recent Samuel Smiths addition as is the fixed seating.  \r\n\r\nOff to the left of the lobby bar the gents is the original 1930s one with three large urinals, original mainly white tiles on the walls to picture-frame height and tiled floor. All other toilets have been modernised.		t	Listed Status: Not listed	53.76015	-1.634487
