oom called Café Merlot, a restaurant called Number 6 (both now run as a separate business) with their own bars, also other bars with a Gothic theme and a night club called Level 7. \r\n\r\nSome details from the Belfast Telegraph		t	Listed Status: B	54.345776	-7.640263
